Home

Welcome to the official website and official home of BONDI MUSIC SCHOOL. Obviously you’ve come here because you are interested in learning how to play a musical instrument, so make yourself at home, feel free to look around and get a feel for what we do here at BMS. Check out our story, videos, photos, rates and testimonials, then get in touch! We are more than happy to chat and work out what we can do to make music part of your life!

Have a nice day. X BMS
